title: New Dawn Giclée Print
short_description: Soft morning light breaking over the horizon, captured in a luminous giclée print.
description_long: New Dawn captures that quiet moment when night finally releases its hold and the first light spills over the horizon. Gentle color shifts and soft edges invite you to pause, breathe, and remember that every day brings a new beginning. This open edition Giclée print is available in two sizes, each hand-matted in a classic white mat, ready to frame and hang in your home or office.
seo_title: New Dawn Giclée Print | P.Forbes Art
seo_meta_description: Bring the calm glow of first light into your home with New Dawn, an open edition giclée print by Patricia Forbes, available matted in 11x14 and 8x10 sizes.
